---
title: Double Caribbean Pork & Slaw Tacos with Charred Corn & Mayonnaise
description: Can’t it be taco night every night? How can you improve on Caribbean-style honey-tossed pork loin, charred corn salsa and crunchy slaw wrapped up in a warm tortilla. We dare you to name a better meal!

*This recipe is under 550kcal per serving.*
